  "prompt": "I'm a shy guy and don't know how to talk to strangers. How do I make new friends at college?",
  "response": "Here are some tips for making friends in college:\n\n1. Join clubs and student organizations related to your interests\n2. Participate in study groups\n3. Talk to classmates before or after class\n4. Attend campus events and social activities\n5. Be open and approachable\n6. Start with small conversations\n7. Use common spaces like the library or student center\n8. Consider taking group classes like fitness or art\n9. Be yourself and don't try too hard\n10. Use social media or campus apps to connect with people\n\nRemember, many other students are looking to make friends too. Take small steps and be patient with yourself.",
